570
00:42:36,730 --> 00:42:37,730
Show yourself.

571
00:42:43,420 --> 00:42:44,420
Hurry up.

572
00:42:47,440 --> 00:42:48,860
I miss you.

573
00:43:19,920 --> 00:43:20,920
I

574
00:43:24,080 --> 00:43:25,220
I miss you too.

575
00:43:43,080 --> 00:43:44,600
I miss you.

576
00:43:57,930 --> 00:43:58,930
You

577
