why did you leave me?

578
00:44:12,920 --> 00:44:13,920
As for me,

579
00:44:14,750 --> 00:44:16,840
I didn't want to trouble Dao
and make him move out,

580
00:44:18,490 --> 00:44:21,020
so I rented the room across instead.

581
00:44:23,620 --> 00:44:24,620
So?

582
00:44:26,800 --> 00:44:27,800
Pretty cool, right?

583
00:44:33,140 --> 00:44:34,280
That way we can stay close.

584
00:44:37,360 --> 00:44:38,590
On the way here, I

585
